T1  - The Glory and Tyranny of Citation Impact: An East Asian Perspective
AU  - Leung, Kwok
Y1  - 2007/06/01
PY  - 2007
DA  - 2007/06/01
N1  - doi: 10.5465/amj.2007.25525592
